content: borisudovicic: Focused on project planning and defining new work streams within the elizaos/eliza repository. This month, their contributions consisted of creating 12 issues to scope out new features and infrastructure. This included initiating work on a rate-limited LLM endpoint (#5438), defining requirements for new agents (#5494, #5767), and outlining plans for a v2/v3 benchmark suite (#5764) and telemetry for training data (#5772).
